<topic xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
    xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="5.1">
    <info>
        <title>Note beams</title>
    </info>
    <para>To beam two 8th or 16th notes, write two dots <code>..</code> after the second note. Both
        notes need to have the same orientation before they can be beamed. Currently only pairs of
        notes can be beamed.</para>
    <example>
        <title>Example</title>
        <para>
            <informaltable>
                <tgroup cols="2">
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Input</entry>
                            <entry>Rendered</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry><code>,  dh sj..  d^h^ s^..j  d^h s^..j^..,</code></entry>
                            <entry/>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </informaltable>
        </para>
    </example>
</topic>
